<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17851880288385379354">Eowyn Ivey&apos;s first novel, The Snow Child, was a finalist for the Pulitzer Prize in fiction and an international bestseller. Her newest novel To the Bright Edge of the World will be released August 2, 2016. Eowyn was raised in Alaska and continues to live there with her husband and two daughters. <br/><br/>Learn more:<br/><a href='http://www.facebook.com/people/Eowyn-Ivey/100002354117696' rel='nofollow noopener'>Facebook</a><br/>Blog: <a href='http://lettersfromalaska.wordpress.com/author/eowynivey/' rel='nofollow noopener'>Letters from Alaska</a><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText17851880288385379354" style="display:none">Eowyn Ivey's first novel, The Snow Child, was a finalist for the Pulitzer Prize in fiction and an international bestseller. Her newest novel To the Bright Edge of the World will be released August 2, 2016. Eowyn was raised in Alaska and continues to live there with her husband and two daughters. <br /><br />Learn more:<br /><a href="http://www.facebook.com/people/Eowyn-Ivey/100002354117696" rel="nofollow noopener">Facebook</a><br />Blog: <a href="http://lettersfromalaska.wordpress.com/author/eowynivey/" rel="nofollow noopener">Letters from Alaska</a><br /></span>
